attributeSource.infoString2: Mulinix INC. d.b.a. Keller Williams Realty, Norman

data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom plus study home in an established neighborhood with its own park and in walking distance to Cobblestone Creek Golf Course. Entertaining will be easy with plenty of room in the living and kitchen areas. Even more space can be utilized out the back door on the large deck. Back inside, you will find the study near the front door. 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom are on one side of the home and another bedroom and the owner's suite on either side of the kitchen. Enjoy the jetted tub, redone shower and large walk-in closet in the owner's suite. The kitchen was recently redone as well. Plenty of storage throughout. This home is located near the University of Oklahoma (approx. 3 miles), tons of restaurants and shopping, and approximately 5 miles to I-35.
